com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.transfer.model

Class CopyResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.transfer.model.CopyResult

  • public class CopyResult
extends Object
    Contains information returned by Amazon S3 for a completed copy operation.

    See TransferManager for more information about creating transfers.

    See Also:
    TransferManager.copy(String, String, String, String), TransferManager.copy(com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.s3.model.CopyObjectRequest)
